The Great Google Gandering

One player is the Great Google Ganger'r

The Great Google Gander'r picks a page in the atlas, and selects a satelite viewable area on that page.
Players are shown a picture of the area.

    *Each player gets to ask the Great Google Gander'r 3 yes or no questions about the area.

Once all questions are asked, players mark a point on the map where they think the area is.
Finally, the Great Google Gander'r plants a point on the map where the actual area is, then measuring the points to 
determine who is closest.

Closest Player => 3pts
Second Closest => 2pts
Thrid Closest => 1pt

*All players not on the podium take two drinks.

Players continue playing until all players have played as the Great Google Gander'r

*Winning is the player who earned the most points during the phase. If tied players compete in a flash round to determine the winner!